title: Ep. - 333 - REALITY STEVE ON BACHELOR NATION CHAOS
description:
Reality Steve reports on Chris Harrison stepping aside temporarily as The Bachelor host, what will happen with the next season of The Bachelorette, why Matt James was a horrible choice, and some of the show’s couples.

 

Jen is back to discuss unsolved mysteries including the death of Elisa Lam, Chris Metallic, and Anna Nicole Smith.
